球季開始之前，卡素爾表示他相信般尼可避免降班至英冠<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/4539267.Carlisle__Burnley_are_more_than_just_a_promotion_fairytale/ | title = Carlisle: Burnley are more than just a promotion fairytale | author = Geldard, Suzanne | publisher = Lancashire Telegraph | date = 2009-08-11 | accessdate = 2009-12-05 | archive-date = 2012-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121009031604/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/4539267.Carlisle__Burnley_are_more_than_just_a_promotion_fairytale/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。8月15日，他被選入般尼自33年來首次於頂級聯賽的賽事的正選名單中，球會最終在[[不列顛尼亞球場|不列顛尼亞球場]]以0-2的比分不敵[[史篤城足球會|史篤城]]。其後，他在般尼的首場英超勝仗亦有上陣—以1-0的比分在摩亞球場擊敗衛冕冠軍[[曼聯足球會|曼聯]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/4176221.Blackpool_0_Burnley_1__Coyle_praises_patient_Carlisle/ | title = Burnley FC 1, Manchester United 0 | publisher = Burnley Express | date = 2009-08-19 | accessdate = 2009-12-18 | archive-date = 2012-10-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121009031530/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/football/4176221.Blackpool_0_Burnley_1__Coyle_praises_patient_Carlisle/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。球季早段，他與新球員[[安德雷·比基|安德雷·比基]]成為防線拍擋。10月3日，他在以2-1的比分擊敗[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰]]的賽事中再次與史提芬·卡達維搭擋<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/MatchReport/0,,10413~47670,00.html | title = Burnley 2–1 Birmingham | date = 2009-10-03 | publisher = Burnley FC | accessdate = 2010-01-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091006025326/http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/MatchReport/0,,10413~47670,00.html | archivedate = 2009-10-06 }}</ref>。12月20日，他在客場不敵[[狼隊足球會|狼隊]]的賽事中鼠蹊受傷，使他在[[聖誕節|聖誕節]]期間缺陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/LatestHeadlines/0,,10413~1912329,00.html | title = Christmas Day Duty For Eager Clarets | date = 2009-12-22 | publisher = Burnley FC | accessdate = 2010-01-07 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100302164557/http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/LatestHeadlines/0%2C%2C10413~1912329%2C00.html | archivedate = 2010-03-02 }}</ref>。他因傷缺陣一個月後，他於2010年1月26日於新帥{{Link-en|白賴仁·羅斯|Brian Laws}}麾下在以0-1的比分不敵[[保頓足球會|保頓]]的賽事中首次上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/MatchReport/0,,10413~48186,00.html | title = Burnley 0–1 Bolton | date = 2010-01-26 | accessdate = 2010-01-26 | publisher = Burnley FC | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100130013316/http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/MatchReport/0,,10413~48186,00.html | archivedate = 2010-01-30 }}</ref>。最終般尼仍難逃降班厄運，來季返回[[英冠|英冠]]作賽。

2011年7月14日，剛降班[[英甲|英甲]]的[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]借用卡素爾一個球季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9534865.stm |title=Clarke Carlisle joins Preston North End on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-14 |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2011-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715021819/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/9534865.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 國際賽 ==

當卡素爾效力[[昆士柏流浪足球會|昆士柏流浪]]時，他曾代表[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]上陣3次。2000年8月31日，他被[[侯活·韋健遜|侯活·韋健遜]]徵召出戰在[[河畔球場|河畔球場]]以6-1的比分大勝[[格魯吉亞21歲以下國家足球隊|格魯吉亞U21]]的賽事中入替而處子上陣<ref name="U21">{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.englandfootballonline.com/TeamBlack/PlyrsBlckMtchUsage/PlyrsBlackU21.html | title = England U21 Black Players | publisher = England Football Online | accessdate = 2009-12-05 | archive-date = 2011-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111108120550/http://englandfootballonline.com/TeamBlack/PlyrsBlckMtchUsage/PlyrsBlackU21.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。第二次代表英格蘭U21上陣亦是入替，他在[[派迪公園球場|派迪公園球場]]以1-1逼和[[德國21歲以下國家足球隊|德國U21]]的2002年[[歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]外圍賽中上陣<ref name="U21"/>。四日後，他在[[瓦爾凱阿科斯基|瓦爾凱阿科斯基]]的{{Link-en|特赫坦·肯塔球場|Tehtaan kenttä}}對[[芬蘭21歲以下國家足球隊|芬蘭U21]]的賽事中最後一次代表英格蘭U21上陣<ref name="U21"/>。儘管，他在下半場表現不俗<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2000/oct/11/newsstory.sport7 | title = Smith off to blot his copybook | publisher = The Guardian | author = Plummer, David | date = 2000-10-11 | accessdate = 2010-01-18 }}</ref>，不過他之後再未有被徵召。

== 踢球風格 ==

卡素爾最擅長的位置是[[中堅|中堅]]。他曾說作為一個年輕人，他模仿了一些後衛的踢球風格，例如[[史提夫·布魯士|史提夫·布魯士]]和[[加利·巴里斯達|加利·巴里斯達]]<ref name="style">{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.watfordfc.com/page/NewsDetail/0,,10400~758814,00.html | title = On the spot with Clarke Carlisle | date = 2005-12-22 | publisher = Watford FC | accessdate = 2010-01-05 }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。然而，他說他們的風格對於現代足球來說過於粗野，他現在試圖觀察對方的進攻模式，與[[約翰·泰利|約翰·泰利]]一樣<ref name="style"/>。他並不擅長於調整速度<ref name="carling">{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.carling.com/football/burnley-fc/clarke-carlisle.html | title = Clarke Carlsile profile | publisher = Carling | accessdate = 2010-01-05 | archive-date = 2012-04-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120405190056/http://www.carling.com/football/burnley-fc/clarke-carlisle.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，這使他有些犯規問題，他在其職業生涯已領紅八次。前列斯聯隊友[[米高·杜貝利|米高·杜貝利]]曾形容他為「強勁」的後衛<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.leedsunited.com/news/duberry-begins-new-chapter-at-united-20040805_2247585_848253 | title = Duberry Begins New Chapter At United | date = 2004-08-05 | publisher = Leeds United AFC | accessdate = 2010-01-05 }}</ref>。此外，他亦是一位被公認為非常聰明的球員，他在中路防守上給人深刻印象的外形，這有賴於他6英尺3[[英吋|英吋]]（1.91米）的身高<ref name="carling"/>。他亦利用其身形優勢，通過主罰[[自由球|自由球]]和[[角球|角球]]等[[死球|死球]]來進攻<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/LatestHeadlines/0,,10413~1092633,00.html | title = Clarke Carlisle is a Claret! | date = 2007-08-17 | publisher = Burnley FC | accessdate = 2010-01-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20120722171603/http://www.burnleyfootballclub.com/page/LatestHeadlines/0,,10413~1092633,00.html | archivedate = 2012-07-22 }}</ref>。截至2010年1月，他已經取得26個聯賽入球。他被形容為「防禦的關鍵」（defensive lynchpin）<ref name="carling"/>。

== 慈善和媒體工作 ==

卡素爾是「踢走它計劃」（Kick It Out Scheme）的大使，這項運動是提倡在足球要包容和平等<ref name="indClarkeCarlisle"/>。他亦是[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]]管理委員會的成員之一<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.givemefootball.com/pfa/about-the-pfa/management-committee | title = Management Committee | publisher = Professional Footballers' Association | accessdate = 2009-12-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100102105421/http://givemefootball.com/pfa/about-the-pfa/management-committee | archivedate = 2010-01-02 }}</ref>，這項工作旨在改善和保護職業足球員地位<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.givemefootball.com/pfa/about-the-pfa/introduction | work = About the PFA | title = Introduction | publisher = Professional Footballers' Association | accessdate = 2009-12-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100209030411/http://www.givemefootball.com/pfa/about-the-pfa/introduction | archivedate = 2010-02-09 }}</ref>，2010年11月17日他接替[[克里斯·鲍威尔|克里斯·鲍威尔]]成為主席<ref>{{cite web | language = en | url = http://www.givemefootball.com/pfa/burnley-skipper-is-unveiled-as-new-pfa-chairman | title = Clarke Carlisle announced as worthy successor to Chris Powell | date = 2010-11-17 | accessdate = 2010-11-17 | publisher = [[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|''givemefootball.com'']] | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110613154611/http://www.givemefootball.com/pfa/burnley-skipper-is-unveiled-as-new-pfa-chairman | archivedate = 2011-06-13 }}</ref>。他在PFA的其中一部分的工作是收集由他跟進的球員的意見並向委員會報告<ref name="PFAwork">{{en}}{{cite web | url = http://www.givemefootball.com/pfa/pfa-news/interview-with-a-pfa-management-committee-member | title = Burnley's Clarke Carlisle is enjoying all aspects of his work | author = Madden, Lawrie | date = 2009-11-19 | publisher = Professional Footballers' Association | accessdate = 2009-12-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110613202342/http://www.givemefootball.com/pfa/pfa-news/interview-with-a-pfa-management-committee-member | archivedate = 2011-06-13 }}</ref>。他還參觀當地學校並舉辦講座與學生對話<ref name="PFAwork"/>。在他的球員生涯結束後，他考慮擔任教學相關工作<ref name="indClarkeCarlisle"/>。

2009年10月，卡素爾出席BBC電視足球節目《{{Link-en|賽後一日|Match of the Day 2}}》<ref name="indClarkeCarlisle">{{en}}{{cite news | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/clarke-carlisle-i-dont-know-why-i-started-to-drink-1804227.html | title = Clarke Carlisle: 'I don't know why I started to drink' | author = Herbert, Ian | date = 2009-10-17 | accessdate = 2009-12-04 | publisher = The Independent | archive-date = 2009-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091020091844/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/premier-league/clarke-carlisle-i-dont-know-why-i-started-to-drink-1804227.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 私生活 ==

從很小的時候，卡素爾就因父母的關係而信奉[[基督教|基督教]]<ref name="dailymail"/>。他接受那些教義並在屈福特期間開始成為一個經常去做禮拜的人<ref name="indClarkeCarlisle"/>。他與潔瑪（Gemma），他們是在卡素爾入住體育機會診所前夕相遇的。截至2009年，他們與在2007年出世的兒子馬利（Marley）一同居住在{{Link-en|裡彭登|Ripponden}}<ref name="indClarkeCarlisle"/> 。他亦有一名在1999年1月出世的女兒法蘭西卡（Francesca），是他與以前的伴侶所生的<ref name="indClarkeCarlisle"/>。

2002年1月30日，卡素爾在電視測驗中獲得「英國腦筋最好的足球員」（Britain's Brainiest Footballer）的銜頭<ref name="brainiest">{{en}}{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/funny_old_game/1793846.stm | title = Clever clogs Clarke | date = 2002-01-31 | accessdate = 2009-12-04 | publisher = BBC Sport | archive-date = 2003-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20030924100846/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/funny_old_game/1793846.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2010年2月24日，他以選手身份參加[[英國第四台|英國第四台]]的遊戲節目《{{Link-en|倒數 (遊戲節目)|Countdown (game show)|倒數}}》並擊敗衛冕冠軍而贏得首場-{比}-賽，使他得以留下<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |last=Murray |first=Scott |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/tvandradioblog/2010/feb/24/premierleague-burnley |title=Countdown, with Burnley's Clarke Carlisle — as it happened |work=Football |publisher=The Guardian Online |date= |accessdate=2010-02-25 |archive-date=2010-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100227020621/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/tvandradioblog/2010/feb/24/premierleague-burnley |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其後，他再次獲勝，取得比前日更高的分數。2月26日，他在第三場終於以3分之差被擊敗<ref>{{en}}{{Cite web | url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/leisure/latest/5025319.Burnley_defender_beaten_on_Countdown_on_day_three/ | title=Burnley defender beaten on Countdown on day three | first=Jon | last=Livesey | work=Lancashire Telegraph | publisher=Newsquest Media Group | date=2010-02-26 | accessdate=2010-03-01 | archive-date=2010-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304111228/http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/leisure/latest/5025319.Burnley_defender_beaten_on_Countdown_on_day_three/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

卡素爾涉嫌於2011年7月29日清晨醉駕<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-lancashire-14556789 |title='Brainiest' footballer Clarke Carlisle on drink-drive charge |publisher=[[BBC|''BBC News'']] |date=2011-08-17 |accessdate=2011-10-13 |archive-date=2011-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110818201321/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-lancashire-14556789 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在10月12日承認控罪，罰款超過2,000英鎊及停牌20個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-lancashire-15279360 |title=Burnley's Clarke Carlisle gets drink-drive ban |publisher=[[BBC|BBC News]] |date=2011-10-12 |accessdate=2011-10-13 |archive-date=2011-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111013204821/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-lancashire-15279360 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

